title: #92Noon!  Wobby/Gannon /Rodriguez
description: 9-Noon is live from TCO Performance Center & football focused as Wobby joins the show for some Vikings deep dives, former NFL MVP Rich Gannon calls in to discuss the AFC West in-depth, & Vikings Assistant Defensive Line Coach Robert Rodriguez tells a touching story about how a recent national tragedy hit home.
